{"ts":1779703330818,"jobId":"e8c10b17-70a7-4507-a721-d15cfe22935e","action":"finished","status":"ok","summary":"I've analyzed the nightly session cleanup cron job in detail. Here's what I found:\n\n## Current Status\n- **Job**: \"Nightly session cleanup\" (ID: e8c10b17-70a7-4507-a721-d15cfe22935e)\n- **Schedule**: Daily at 3:00 AM America/Los_Angeles time (10:00 UTC)\n- **Command**: `openclaw sessions cleanup --enforce`\n- **Cleanup criteria**: Idle subagents (3+ hours), direct sessions (1+ day)\n- **Last run**: Successful, completed in ~26 seconds\n- **Delivery**: No notifications configured (mode: \"none\")\n- **Current sessions**: 0 active sessions visible\n\n## Run History Analysis\nThe job has been running successfully for at least 16 consecutive days. Early runs had Telegram delivery errors (when notifications were attempted but no chatId was configured), but those have been resolved by setting delivery mode to \"none\".\n\n## Potential Considerations\n\n1. **No notifications**: If cleanup fails or removes important sessions, there's no alert system\n2. **Fixed thresholds**: 3 hours for subagents might interrupt some long-running tasks\n3. **Timezone impact**: 3:00 AM LA time = 6:00 PM in Tokyo (potentially working hours)\n4. **No dry run option**: Can't preview what will be cleaned before enforcement\n5. **Error reporting**: No failure alerts if cleanup encounters issues\n\n## What would you like me to do next?\n\nI can:\n1. **Run a manual cleanup test** to see what the command actually does\n2. **Check session logs** to see what was cleaned in previous runs\n3. **Add notifications** to the cron job (Telegram, Discord, etc.)\n4. **Adjust cleanup thresholds** (e.g., increase subagent timeout to 6+ hours)\n5. **Add failure alerts** to catch cleanup issues\n6. **Create a weekly dry run** to preview cleanup without enforcement\n7. **Review the actual cleanup command behavior** by examining OpenClaw's session management\n\nWhat would be most helpful for you?","deliveryStatus":"not-requested","delivery":{"intended":{"channel":"last","to":null,"source":"last"},"fallbackUsed":false,"delivered":false},"sessionId":"8906d411-50a3-4683-9f57-8c92f0f0e603","sessionKey":"agent:dj:cron:e8c10b17-70a7-4507-a721-d15cfe22935e:run:8906d411-50a3-4683-9f57-8c92f0f0e603","runAtMs":1779703200183,"durationMs":130621,"nextRunAtMs":1779789600000,"model":"deepseek-3.2","provider":"kiro","usage":{"input_tokens":939,"output_tokens":3431,"total_tokens":374}}
